391
00:23:09,200 --> 00:23:11,700
<i>That's right, Little Aunt. I agree.</i>

392
00:23:11,700 --> 00:23:14,900
I think a long courtship isn't good.

393
00:23:14,900 --> 00:23:20,000
You might as well discover some of that mystery in marriage.

394
00:23:20,900 --> 00:23:22,900
