I don't mind liking you for another 20 years,

414
00:24:49,900 --> 00:24:54,700
30 years, 50 years, or even longer.

415
00:25:00,100 --> 00:25:03,600
Miss Zheng Duoxi, will you marry me?

416
00:25:04,900 --> 00:25:08,200
For richer, for poorer,

417
00:25:08,200 --> 00:25:11,500
