420
00:25:19,300 --> 00:25:21,600
I, Qi Heng, will not go back on my word.

421
00:25:22,600 --> 00:25:24,600
Will you marry me?

422
00:25:39,800 --> 00:25:42,900
- Pinky swear.
- Pinky swear.

423
00:25:42,900 --> 00:25:45,000
- Promise.
- Promise.

